TEMPLATE 1: STANDARD SAAS / PRODUCT WEBSITE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# [Brand Name]

> [Brand Name] is a [one-sentence product description, e.g., generative SEO tool].

## Core Features
- [Feature 1]: [Brief feature description]
- [Feature 2]: [Brief feature description]
- [Feature 3]: [Brief feature description]

## Key Resources
- [Pricing](/pricing): Subscription tiers and credit structures.
- [Documentation](/docs): Developer API references and guides.
- [Support](/support): Customer helpdesk and contact channels.

